%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amidst%20News%20of%20Retirement%20From%20Public%20Life%2C%20Manmohan%20Singh's%20Work%20Lauded%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F09142140%2FMMS.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Manmohan%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20tenure%20as%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20is%20set%20to%20end%20in%20April%20this%20year.%20The%2091-year-old%20former%20prime%20minister%20is%20likely%20to%20retire%20from%20public%20life%20owing%20to%20his%20frail%20health%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-a-storied-career-former-pm-manmohan-singh-likely-to-retire-from-public-life-101707451386261.html%5C%22%3Ethe%C2%A0%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%20citing%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20is%20mentally%20well%2C%20but%20finds%20it%20difficult%20to%20move%E2%80%A6his%20return%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20is%20out%20of%20the%20question%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20newspaper%20quoted%20a%20close%20aide%20of%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20also%20said%20that%20Singh%20told%20his%20Congress%20party%20he%20wished%20to%20quit%20his%20Rajya%20Sabha%20membership%20around%20a%20year%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSingh%20felt%20that%20there%20was%20no%20point%20continuing%20if%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20able%20to%20discharge%20his%20duties%20fully%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20person%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20last%20few%20appearances%20in%20parliament%2C%20Singh%20was%20seen%20using%20a%20wheelchair%20for%20mobility.%20According%20to%20his%20profile%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fsansad.in%2Frs%2Fmembers%5C%22%3ERajya%20Sabha%E2%80%99s%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20last%20attended%20parliament%20on%20December%205%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%E2%80%99s%20latest%20stint%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20began%20as%20an%20MP%20for%20Rajasthan%20in%20August%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Rajya%20Sabha%20legislators%20have%20a%20term%20of%20six%20years%2C%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20tenure%20ends%20in%20April%20this%20year%20as%20he%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fmanmohan-singh-takes-oath-as-rajya-sabha-member-from-rajasthan-5929632%2F%5C%22%3Eserving%20the%20remainder%20of%20a%20term%3C%2Fa%3E%20started%20by%20BJP%20MP%20Madan%20Lal%20Saini%2C%20who%20was%20elected%20to%20the%20seat%20in%20March%202018%20but%20died%20in%20June%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20first%20elected%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20as%20an%20Assam%20MP%20in%201991.%20He%20continued%20to%20represent%20the%20state%20till%20June%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20prime%20minister%20between%202004%20and%202014%2C%20Singh%20presided%20over%20landmark%20legislation%20such%20as%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20Act%20and%20the%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act%20as%20well%20as%20over%20a%20fast-growing%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20infamous%202G%20spectrum%20and%20Commonwealth%20Games%20scams%2C%20which%20played%20a%20major%20role%20in%20the%20fall%20of%20the%20Congress-led%20Union%20government%2C%20also%20took%20place%20on%20his%20watch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20parliamentarians%2C%20including%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20recognised%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20work%20while%20giving%20a%20farewell%20to%20retiring%20Rajya%20Sabha%20members%20during%20the%20ongoing%20budget%20session%20of%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20some%20select%20parliamentarians%20will%20be%20discussed%20when%20our%20democracy%20is%20talked%20about%2C%20the%20respected%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20contributions%20will%20surely%20figure%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHi67xhHFwmc%5C%22%3EModi%20said%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday%20(February%208).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20also%20spoke%20of%20a%20time%20when%20Singh%20appeared%20in%20a%20wheelchair%20to%20cast%20his%20vote%20on%20an%20issue%20even%20when%20%E2%80%9Cit%20was%20clear%20the%20treasury%20benches%20would%20win%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20question%20of%20who%20he%20came%20to%20strengthen.%20I%20take%20it%20he%20came%20to%20strengthen%20democracy%2C%E2%80%9D%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20opposition%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20thanked%20Modi%20for%20%E2%80%9Ccomplimenting%E2%80%9D%20the%20good%20work%20Singh%20had%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20leader%20H.D.%20Deve%20Gowda%20said%20Singh%20was%20%E2%80%9Chonest%20to%20the%20core%E2%80%9D%20and%20claimed%20he%20was%20defamed%20for%20wrongdoing%20by%20others%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Frajya-sabha-bids-farewell-to-ex-prime-minister-manmohan-singh-after-33-years-in-house%2Fcid%2F1999249%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20report%2C%20Singh%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20saying%20he%20was%20unable%20to%20attend%20a%20dinner%20for%20retiring%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20he%20was%20prime%20minister%2C%20Singh%20was%20also%20leader%20of%20opposition%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20the%20Union%20finance%20minister%2C%20the%20deputy%20chairman%20of%20the%20Planning%20Commission%20and%20the%20governor%20of%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India.%20He%20also%20worked%20in%20the%20United%20Nations%20Secretariat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20oversaw%20the%20liberalisation%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20economy%20as%20finance%20minister%20in%20the%20early%201990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Singh%20has%20been%20described%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Caccidental%20prime%