.08%25E2%2580%25AFPM.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F09141737%2FScreenshot-2024-02-09-at-2.16.08%25E2%2580%25AFPM-300x178.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F09141737%2FScreenshot-2024-02-09-at-2.16.08%25E2%2580%25AFPM-1024x608.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-696345%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22712%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20tally%20for%20the%20National%20Assembly%20is%20at%20the%20bottom%2C%20where%20the%20PTI%20independents%20are%2066%20to%20PML(N)%E2%80%99s%2044.%20The%20assembly%20seats%20of%20Punjab%2C%20Sindh%2C%20Balochistan%20and%20KPK%20are%20clockwise%20from%20top%20left.%20Photo%3A%20Geo%20News%20screengrab.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Punjab%20assembly%2C%20the%20PTI%20independents%20and%20Sharif%E2%80%99s%20PML(N)%20are%20neck-and-neck%20at%2093%20and%2089%20seats%2C%20according%20to%20Geo%20TV%E2%80%99s%20broadcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20Peoples%20Party%20under%20Bilawal%20Bhutto%20Zardari%20is%20sweeping%20the%20Sindh%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPML-N%20leader%20Maryam%20Nawaz%2C%20Sharif%E2%80%99s%20daughter%2C%20has%20won%20from%20her%20seat%20in%20Lahore%20with%2083%2C855%20votes%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EDawn%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PTI%20independents%20%E2%80%93%20PTI%20were%20the%20winners%20of%20the%20last%20election%20%E2%80%93%20are%20outperforming%20expectations%20by%20leading%20in%20many%20constituencies.%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20party%20has%20been%20barred%20from%20participating%20in%20the%20election%20as%20a%20bloc%2C%20but%20individuals%20endorsed%20by%20his%20party%20entered%20the%20race%20as%20independent%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20initial%20post-poll%20trends%20charted%20PTI%E2%80%99s%20strong%20showing%2C%20many%20results%20were%20%E2%80%98frozen%E2%80%99%20overnight.%20By%203%20am%20on%20February%208%2C%20more%20than%2010%20hours%20after%20polls%20closed%2C%20only%20four%20provincial%20assembly%20results%20had%20been%20announced.%20The%20delay%20has%20been%20blamed%20on%20%E2%80%9Cinternet%20problems%E2%80%9D%20after%20the%20closure%20by%20authorities%20of%20internet%20and%20phone%20access%20during%20the%20day.%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20interior%20ministry%20has%20cited%20the%20fact%20that%20two%20days%20ago%2C%20two%20explosions%20by%20the%20ISIS%20had%20led%20to%2028%20deaths%20as%20reason%20for%20this%20shutdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1812507%2Fin-the-dark%5C%22%3EIn%20an%20editorial%2C%20%3Cem%3EDawn%3C%2Fem%3E%20newspaper%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20move%20rendered%20thousands%20of%20voters%20clueless%20as%20to%20where%20their%20polling%20stations%20were%2C%20as%20the%20ECP%E2%80%99s%208300%20SMS%20service%20could%20only%20be%20operated%20on%20mobile%20networks.%20The%20decision%20not%20only%20defies%20court%20orders%20mandating%20uninterrupted%20internet%20connectivity%20during%20the%20polls%2C%20it%20raises%20a%20glaring%20question%3A%20how%20does%20snapping%20communication%20channels%20deter%20terrorism%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20counting%20resumed%2C%20Nawaz%E2%80%99s%20PML(N)%20started%20to%20win%20seats%20in%20Punjab%20where%20they%20had%20been%20lagging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20of%20Pakistan%20today%20morning%20ordered%20returning%20officers%20to%20speed%20up%20the%20release%20of%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistani%20voters%20went%20to%20the%20election%20polls%20on%20Thursday%2C%20but%20the%20day%20was%20marred%20by%20violence%20and%20the%20suspension%20of%20communication%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistani%20voters%20showed%20themselves%20undeterred%20by%20very%20cold%20weather%20in%20several%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20even%20while%20the%20threat%20of%20violence%20is%20highlighted%20by%20the%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20troops%20deployed%20across%20the%20country.%20However%2C%20pollsters%20predicted%20a%20low%20turnout%20from%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20128%20million%20eligible%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20inputs%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fpakistan-elections-vote-counting-continues-into-friday%2Flive-68209997%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20report%20is%20being%20updated%20and%20republished%20from%20time%20to%20time.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707467431000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-nawaz-sharif-imran-khan-counting-delay-internet%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20initial%20post-poll%20trends%20charted%20a%20strong%20showing%20by%20Imran%20Khan's%20PTI%2C%20many%20results%20were%20'frozen'%20overnight.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22British%20Airways%20to%20restart%20Israel%20flights%20from%20April%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707467340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F22%2F04%2F768x432%2Fskynews-british-airways-flight_5730391.jpg%3F20220406084453%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fbritish-airways-plans-to-restart-israel-flights-from-april-13067243%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22British%20Airways%20(BA)%20has%20revealed%20plans%20to%20resume%20flights%20to%20and%20from%20Israel%2C%20beginning%20in%20April.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fbritish-airways-plans-to-restart-israel-flights-from-april-13067243%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fbritish-airways-plans-to-restart-israel-flights-from-april-13067243%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fbritish-airways-plans-to-restart-israel-flights-from-april-13067243%22%