ment%E2%80%99s%20own%20previous%20assurances.%20For%20instance%2C%20when%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20was%20chief%20minister%20of%20Gujarat%2C%20he%20was%20a%20strong%20supporter%20of%20legalising%20the%20MSP.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Centre%20even%20assured%20us%20of%20this%20step%20as%20part%20of%20the%20farm%20movement%20negotiation%20in%202020%20but%20it%20never%20took%20any%20concrete%20shape%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20have%20also%20asked%20for%20justice%20in%20the%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20murder%20case%20and%20compensation%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20for%20the%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecurity%20stepped%20up%20at%20borders%2C%20notices%20to%20farmers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20believe%20that%20the%20three%20Union%20ministers%20flying%20down%20to%20Chandigarh%20for%20the%20meeting%20was%20because%20of%20looming%20election%20season%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20BJP%2C%20hoping%20to%20win%20a%20third%20consecutive%20term%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20due%20in%20less%20than%20two%20months%2C%20does%20not%20want%20a%20replay%20of%20the%202020%20farm%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Centre%20has%20initiated%20talks%20with%20farm%20unions%2C%20they%20are%20also%20taking%20precautions.%20Security%20is%20being%20beefed%20up%20at%20all%20entries%20points%20towards%20Delhi%20from%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20is%20trying%20its%20level%20best%20to%20convince%20farmers%20to%20defer%20the%20%E2%80%98Delhi%20chalo%E2%80%99%20call.%20But%20if%20their%20programme%20continues%20as%20planned%2C%20the%20government%20is%20also%20taking%20steps%20to%20prevent%20farmers%20from%20reaching%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20that%20the%20police%20are%20keeping%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20the%20movement%20of%20farmers%E2%80%99%20leaders%20heading%20the%20agitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ambala%20police%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20petrol%20pump%20owners%20asking%20them%20not%20to%20give%20petrol%20and%20diesel%20to%20people%20in%20cans%20and%20drums.%20They%20were%20specifically%20asked%20not%20to%20give%20petrol%20and%20diesel%20to%20those%20vehicles%20which%20had%20farmers%E2%80%99%20union%20flags%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Haryana%20Police%20also%20issued%20notices%20to%20around%2020%20leaders%20of%20the%20Bhartiya%20Kisan%20Union%20(Shaheed%20Bhagat%20Singh)%20in%20Ambala%20district.%20A%20farmers%E2%80%99%20union%20leader%2C%20who%20too%20was%20issued%20a%20notice%2C%20said%20that%20the%20Haryana%20Police%20had%20even%20asked%20them%20to%20furnish%20details%20about%20their%20bank%20accounts%20before%20February%2010%2C%20failing%20which%20they%20would%20face%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notices%2C%20which%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20seen%2C%20have%20been%20issued%20under%20Haryana%20Recovery%20of%20Damages%20of%20Property%20During%20Disturbance%20of%20Public%20Order%20Act%202021%20and%20under%20section%2069%20of%20Haryana%20Police%20Act%202007%2C%20under%20which%20it%20was%20mandatory%20to%20take%20permission%20before%20giving%20a%20call%20for%20meeting%20or%20gathering%20on%20the%20road%2C%20which%20was%20public%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E13%20Feb%20Farmers%20Delhi%20March%20Update%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E~Farm%20leaders%20met%203%20GOI%20minister%20delegation%3Cbr%3E%5Cn~Another%20meeting%20expected%20before%2013Feb%3Cbr%3E%5Cn~No%20firm%20commitment%20of%20Govt%20on%20MSP%20Guarantee%20Law%3Cbr%3E%5Cn~Farmers%20call%20of%2013%20Feb%20stands%3Cbr%3E%5Cn~Haryana%20police%20is%20raiding%20farm%20leaders%20houses%2C%20notices%20to%20deter%20farmers%20pasted%20!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fqx6bmlyska%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fqx6bmlyska%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Ramandeep%20Singh%20Mann%20(%40ramanmann1974)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Framanmann1974%2Fstatus%2F1755777442051182792%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%209%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20BKU%20(SBS)%20spokesperson%20Tejveer%20Singh%20Ambala%20had%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20one%20hand%20the%20Haryana%20police%20was%20targeting%20farmers%20by%20issuing%20them%20notices%20and%20asking%20petrol%20pump%20owners%20not%20to%20give%20them%20petrol%20and%20diesel%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20the%20Central%20government%20ministers%20were%20holding%20meetings%20with%20us.%20This%20shows%20that%20Delhi%20fears%20the%20farmers.%20We%20will%20be%20moving%20to%20Delhi%20on%20February%2013.%20We%20have%20won%20the%20battle.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETejveer%20also%20said%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20started%20his%20first%20%E2%80%98Chai%20pe%20Charcha%E2%80%99%20programme%20from%20Yavatmal%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20as%20per%20a%20recent%20report%2C%20the%20number%20of%20farmer%20suicides%20have%20gone%20up%20in%20the%20Marathwada%20region%2C%20which%20shows%20the%20grim%20side%20of%20the%20farm%20crisis%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CFarmers%20do%20not%20want%20to%20create%20trouble%20for%20anybody.%20However%2C%20if%20people%20heading%20to%20IGI%20airport%20or%20those%20going%20to%20weddings%20faced%20trouble%20while%20commuting%20on%20February%2013%2C%20not%20the%20farmers%20but%20the%20Central%20government%20will%20be%20responsible.%20Let%20the%20farmers%20reach%20Delhi%2C%20we%20have%20every%20right%20to%20protest%20and%20inform%20people%20of%20how%20farmers%20were%20being%20ruined%20by%20the%20Modi%20government.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Gramin%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Samiti%20(GKMS)%20president%20Ranjit%20Singh%20Raju%20from%20Sri%20Ganganagar%20district%2C%20Rajasthan%20also%20said%20that%20farmers%20were%20deliberately%20being%20pushed%20into%20the%20debt%20trap%20by%20the%20Modi%20government.%20%E2%80%9CFarmers%20from%20Hanumangarh%2C%20Anoopgarh%20and%20Sri%20Ganganagar%20were%20holding%20tractor%20marches%20for%20the%20February%2013%20Delhi%20Chalo%20protest.%20No%20farmer%20ever%20faces%20scarcity%20of%20wheat%20in%20his%20house.%20A%20farmer%20hardly%20needs%20any%20luxuries%20to%20lead%20his%20life.%20All%20we%20need%20is%20flour%20and%20pickles%20to%20sustain%20and%20rest%20of%20the%20things%20do%20not%20matter.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20all%20are%20participating%20in%20the%20protest%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20200%20farmers%E2%80%99%20unions%20have%20planned%20to%20march%20to%20Delhi%20on%20February%2013%2C%20which%20will%20include%20around%20150%20unions%20of%20SKM%20(non-political)%20and%20around%2076%20unions%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20the%20KMSC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESKM%20(non-political)%20is%20a%20breakaway%20faction%20of%20the%20SKM%2C%20which%20played%20a%20vital%20role%20in%20forcing%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20take%20back%20three%20farm%20laws%20through%20a%20year-long%20protest%20outside%20Delhi%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%202020%20protest%2C%20several%20unions%20in%20SKM%20went%20in%20different%20directions.%20Some%20fought%20elections%20and%20some%20committed%20to%20remain%20non-political.%20SKM%20(non-%20political)%20has%20been%20born%20of%20this%20churning%20and%20claims%20to%20have%20150%20farm%20unions%20as%20members%20from%20Punjab%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20UP%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20West%20Bengal%20and%20other%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKMSC%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20is%20headed%20by%20Sarwan%20Singh%20Pandher%20and%20claims%20to%20have%20the%20support%20of%2050%20farm%20unions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20other%20SKM%20faction%20under%20Dr%20Darshan%20Pal%2C%20Yadvindra%20Yadav%20and%20others%20distanced%20itself%20from%20the%20%E2%80%98Dilli%20Chalo%E2%80%99%20protest%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20last%20week%2C%20SKM%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20national%20coordination%20committee%20of%20SKM%20held%20an%20online%20meeting%20and%20clarified%20that%20SKM%20has%20not%20given%20any%20call%20for%20%E2%80%98Dilli%20Chalo%E2%80%99.%20SKM%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20decision%20of%20certain%20kisan%20organisations%20to%20protest%20in%20Delhi%20on%20February%2013.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20SKM%20leaders%20Balbir%20Singh%20Rajewal%2C%20Darshan%20Pal%20and%20Rakesh%20Tikait%20were%20getting%20ready%20for%20the%20February%2016%20%E2%80%98Gramin%20Bharat%20Bandh%E2%80%99%20across%20the%20country%2C%20BKU%20(Ekta%20Ugrahan)%20president%20Joginder%20Singh%20Ugrahan%20was%20already%20leading%20separate%20protests%20in%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharat%20Bandh%20call%20was%20given%20by%20the%20SKM%2C%20joint%20platform%20of%20Central%20Trade%20Unions%20and%20Independent%20Sectoral%20Federations%20for%20farmers%2C%20all%20workers%20in%20the%20unorganised%20sector%20including%20ASHA%2C%20Anganwadi%20and%20mid-day%20meal%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20message%2C%20BKU%20Rajewal%20president%20Balbir%20Singh%20Rajewal%20appealed%20to%20people%20to%20join%20the%20Bharat%20Bandh%20on%20February%2016%20and%20raise%20voice%20against%20the%20voiceless%20farmers%2C%20small%20shopkeepers%2C%20and%20the%20marginalised%20sections%20of%20the%20society.%20BKU%20leader%20Rakesh%20Tikait%20also%20appealed%20people%20to%20make%20Bharat%20Bandh%20a%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20Kusum%20Arora.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707449904000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F09090639%2FGF0FvlvWQAExf0u.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-groups-confront-modi-govt-on-unfulfilled-promises-3-union-ministers-rush-to-meet-them%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20unions%20have%20said%20they%20will%20march%20to%20Delhi%20on%20February%2013%20if%20their%20demands%20are%20not%20fulfilled.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-groups-confront-modi-govt-on-unfulfilled-promises-3-union-ministers-rush-to-meet-them%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Putin%20questioned%20about%20American%20journalist%20Evan%20Gershkovich%2C%20who%20has%20been%20detained%20in%20Russia%20for%20more%20than%20300%20days%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vladimir%20Putin%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c0e17443bb77284ba3740f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221488%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERussian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20suggested%20Wall%20Street%20Journalist%20Evan%20Gershkovich%20could%20be%20released%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Tucker%20Carlson%20on%20Thursday.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EVladimir%20Putin%20was%20asked%20about%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20reporter%20Evan%20Gershkovich%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Tucker%20Carlson.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPutin%20said%20he%20wants%20Gershkovich%20to%20return%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPutin%20continued%20to%20double%20down%20on%20Russia's%20decision%20to%20charge%20Gershkovich%20with%20espionage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftuckercarlson.com%2Fthe-vladimir-putin-interview%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo-hour-long%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftucker-carlsons-putin-interview-seems-timed-for-maximum-damage-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETucker%20Carlson%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Moscow%20that%20aired%20on%20Thursday%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20said%20he%20would%20%26quot%3Bnot%20rule%20out%26quot%3B%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20reporter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fevan-gershkovich-journalist-jailed-in-russia-100-days-friend-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEvan%20Gershkovich's%3C%2Fa%3E%20release.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20journalist%20has%20been%20awaiting%20trial%20for%20almost%20a%20year%20after%20being%20charged%20with%20espionage%20in%20March%20of%202023.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20done%20so%20many%20gestures%20of%20goodwill%2C%20out%20of%20decency%2C%20that%20I%20think%20we%20have%20run%20out%20of%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Putin%20said%20after%20the%20former%20Fox%20News%20host%20asked%20at%20the%20end%20of%20a%20lengthy%2C%20often%20rambling%20interview%20if%20he'd%20be%20willing%20to%20release%20Gershkovich%20back%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPutin%20said%20that%20he%20believes%20an%20agreement%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Russia%20regarding%20Gershkovich's%20release%20can%20be%20reached%20and%20that%20the%20two%20countries%20have%20been%20in%20discussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20it%20does%20not%20make%20any%20sense%20to%20keep%20him%20in%20prison%20in%20Russia%2C%26quot%3B%20Putin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20ready%20to%20talk.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20talks%20are%20underway%2C%20and%20there%20have%20been%20many%20successful%20examples%20of%20these%20talks%20crowned%20with%20success.%20Probably%2C%20this%20is%20going%20to%20be%20crowned%20with%20success%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Putin%20continued%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20wants%20Gershkovich%20to%20%26quot%3Breturn%20to%20his%20hometown.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Putin%20said%20he%20would%20not%20rule%20out%20Gershkovich's%20release%2C%20he%20appeared%20to%20double%20down%20on%20charging%20the%20journalist%20with%20espionage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20person%20gets%20secret%20information%20and%20does%20that%20in%20a%20conspiratorial%20manner%2C%20then%20this%20is%20qualified%20as%20espionage%2C%26quot%3B%20Putin%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20Gershkovich%20%26quot%3Bwas%20caught%20red-handed%26quot%3B%20receiving%20%26quot%3Bclassified%2C%20confidential%20information.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDow%20Jones%2C%20The%20Journal%2C%20and%20Gershkovich%20have%20denied%20these%20claims.%20The%20US%20State%20Department%20designated%20Gershkovich%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fu-s-deems-wsj-reporter-evan-gershkovich-wrongfully-detained-by-russia-f1be833%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bwrongfully%20detained%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20chilling%20and%20outrageous%20that%20Evan%20has%20now%20spent%2010%20months%20of%20his%20life%20in%20prison%2C%20simply%20for%20doing%20his%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fworld%2Frussia%2Frussian-court-extends-detention-of-wsj-reporter-evan-gershkovich-0963444b%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDow%20Jones%20and%20the%20Journal%20said%20in%20January%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20adding%20that%20they%20%26quot%3Bdemand%20Evan's%20immediate%20release.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGershkovich%20was%20detained%20by%20Russia's%20Federal%20Security%20Service%20on%20March%2029%20while%20on%20a%20reporting%20trip%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fnews%2Fevan-gershkovich%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Journal%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpaul-whelan-said-doesnt-know-why-hes-still-russian-captivity-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPaul%20Whelan%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20former%20US%20Marine%2C%20was%20sentenced%20to%2016%20years%20in%20prison%20after%20Russia%20charged%20him%20with%20espionage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fv