20of%20colors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20achieve%20its%20high%20contrast%20performance%2C%20the%20U6K%20uses%20a%20Mini%20LED%20backlight%20with%20local%20dimming%2C%20a%20combination%20we%20haven't%20seen%20in%20other%20TVs%20in%20this%20price%20range.%20This%20allows%20the%20screen%20to%20dim%20across%20small%20areas%2C%20so%20dark%20elements%20of%20an%20image%20can%20remain%20dark%2C%20while%20only%20bright%20areas%20get%20bright.%20When%20we%20reviewed%20the%20U6K%2C%20we%20did%20notice%20that%20black%20levels%20weren't%20as%20deep%20and%20uniform%20as%20you'd%20find%20on%20pricier%20displays%2C%20but%20the%20TV%20delivered%20impressive%20picture%20quality%20for%20the%20money.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColors%20are%20also%20vivid%20thanks%20to%20the%20display's%20use%20of%20quantum%20dots%2C%20and%20the%20U6K%20can%20achieve%20a%20peak%20brightness%20of%20600%20nits.%20For%20the%20best%20HDR%20performance%2C%20we%20recommend%20finding%20a%20set%20that%20can%20get%20closer%20to%201%2C000%20nits%20or%20higher%2C%20but%20600%20is%20still%20bright%20enough%20to%20see%20the%20benefits%20that%20high%20dynamic%20range%20videos%20can%20provide.%20The%20U6K%20supports%20every%20major%20HDR%20format%2C%20including%20Dolby%20Vision%2C%20which%20Samsung%20TVs%20lack.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20the%20TV%20looks%20great%20when%20viewed%20from%20a%20centered%20position%2C%20colors%20and%20contrast%20fade%20if%20you%20sit%20off%20to%20the%20side%20of%20the%20display.%20This%20is%20a%20common%20drawback%20for%20many%20budget%20and%20midrange%20TVs%20that%20use%20LED%20and%20QLED%20panels%2C%20so%20we%20recommend%20opting%20for%20an%20OLED%20model%20if%20that's%20a%20dealbreaker.%20The%20U6K's%20smart%20TV%20navigation%20speed%20also%20leaves%20a%20bit%20to%20be%20desired%2C%20and%20its%2060Hz%20panel%20can't%20support%20120Hz%20gameplay%20on%20a%20PS5%20or%20Xbox%20Series%20X.%20But%20again%2C%20these%20are%20expected%20tradeoffs%20for%20a%20budget-friendly%20set%20like%20this.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20the%20U6K%20is%20geared%20toward%20buyers%20who%20want%20an%20affordable%2075-inch%20TV%20that%20doesn't%20sacrifice%20genuine%20HDR%20capabilities%2C%20and%20in%20that%20sense%2C%20it's%20a%20winner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fhisense-u6k-4k-tv-review%5C%22%3EHisense%20U6K%204K%20TV%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20midrange%20display%3Cp%3EThe%20U7K%20is%20Hisense's%20midrange%204K%20QLED%20TV.%20Like%20the%20cheaper%20U6K%2C%20it%20uses%20a%20Mini%20LED%20backlight%20with%20local%20dimming%20and%20quantum%20dots%2C%20but%20the%20U7K%20delivers%20an%20even%20brighter%20image%20and%20deeper%20black%20levels.%20It%20also%20makes%20the%20jump%20from%20a%2060Hz%20panel%20to%20a%20120Hz%20screen%2C%20which%20gives%20this%20model%20better%20gaming%20performance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20our%20review%20process%2C%20the%20U7K%20impressed%20us%20with%20its%20vibrant%20HDR%20images%2C%20and%20it%20offered%20noticeably%20better%20black-level%20performance%20than%20the%20U6K%20and%20other%20cheaper%20QLEDs.%20We%20also%20didn't%20encounter%20any%20major%20blooming%20(when%20halos%20appear%20around%20bright%20objects)%20in%20dark%20scenes%2C%20but%20shadow%20detail%20wasn't%20as%20good%20as%20what%20we've%20seen%20on%20more%20expensive%20TVs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20other%20similar%20QLEDs%2C%20viewing%20angles%20are%20lacking%2C%20so%20you'll%20want%20to%20sit%20centered%20to%20the%20screen%20to%20get%20the%20best%20performance.%20And%20though%20the%20U7K's%20Google%20TV%20interface%20has%20lots%20of%20apps%2C%20it's%20not%20the%20snappiest%20version%20of%20this%20OS%20that%20we've%20used.%20Eagle-eyed%20viewers%20might%20also%20spot%20minor%20uniformity%20issues%20and%20occasional%20brightness%20fluctuations%20from%20scene%20to%20scene%2C%20but%20these%20flaws%20are%20minor%20compared%20to%20the%20TV's%20many%20strengths.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20perfect%2C%20but%20the%20U7K%20is%20the%20best%2075-inch%20TV%20for%20people%20who%20want%20upper-midrange%20performance%20without%20breaking%20the%20bank.%20It%20has%20a%20list%20price%20of%20about%20%241%2C200%2C%20but%20it's%20often%20sold%20for%20%24900%2C%20which%20is%20a%20fantastic%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fhisense-u7k-4k-tv-review%5C%22%3EHisense%20U7K%204K%20TV%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20brightness%3Cp%3EShoppers%20who%20want%20a%20bright%2075-inch%20TV%20to%20deliver%20great%20daytime%20viewing%20and%20intense%20HDR%20performance%20should%20have%20the%20TCL%20QM8%20on%20the%20top%20of%20their%20list.%20This%20TV%20can%20hit%20over%202%2C000%20nits%2C%20which%20puts%20it%20among%20the%20absolute%20brightest%20displays%20on%20the%20market.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20Hisense%20U7K%2C%20this%20TCL%20display%20uses%20a%20Mini%20LED%20backlight%20with%20local%20dimming%2C%20quantum%20dots%2C%20and%20a%20fast%20144Hz%20refresh%20for%20PC%20games.%20But%20this%20model%20has%20more%20dimming%20zones%2C%20which%20enables%20it%20to%20deliver%20even%20more%20precise%20control%20over%20its%20light%20output.%20When%20reviewing%20the%20TV%2C%20we%20were%20blown%20away%20by%20the%20display's%20deep%20black%20levels%20and%20vibrant%20colors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20QM8's%20contrast%20control%20still%20can't%20match%20an%20OLED%2C%20it%20gets%20remarkably%20close%20while%20offering%20a%20brighter%20image.%20This%20makes%20it%20an%20especially%20good%20choice%20for%20people%20who%20like%20to%20watch%20TV%20during%20the%20day%20since%20you%20can%20pump%20up%20the%20brightness%20to%20overcome%20ambient%20lighting%20and%20sunlight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20while%20the%20screen's%20anti-reflective%20coding%20works%20incredibly%20well%20in%20most%20cases%2C%20it%20uses%20a%20filter%20that%20can%20cause%20a%20subtle%20rainbow%20effect%20when%20hit%20with%20light%20from%20certain%20angles.%20(This%20rainbow%20streaking%20is%20also%20common%20on%20many%20Samsung%20QLED%20TVs%20and%20shows%20up%20most%20when%20overhead%20lighting%20is%20near%20the%20screen.)%20If%20that's%20the%20case%20for%20your%20setup%2C%20you%20might%20want%20to%20consider%20a%20different%20model%20on%20our%20list.%20And%20though%20viewing%20angles%20are%20a%20bit%20better%20than%20the%20cheaper%20QLED%20TVs%20we%20recommend%2C%20they're%20still%20not%20as%20good%20as%20what%20you%20get%20with%20an%20OLED.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Ftcl-qm8-qled-4k-tv-review%5C%22%3ETCL%20QM8%204K%20TV%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20premium%20option%3Cp%3ESony's%20A95L%20OLED%20is%20the%20ultimate%20display%20for%20big%20home%20theater%20enthusiasts%20who%20want%20a%2077-inch%20TV.%20Bar%20none%2C%20this%20is%20the%20most%20impressive%20TV%20we've%20tested%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20one%20of%20the%20most%20expensive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20our%20top%20pick%20in%20this%20guide%2C%20the%20Samsung%20S89C%2C%20the%20Sony%20A95L%20uses%20a%20QD-OLED%20panel%20with%20an%20infinite%20contrast%20ratio%20and%20high%20color%20volume.%20But%20while%20the%20S89C%20tops%20out%20at%20around%201%2C000%20nits%20of%20peak%20brightness%2C%20we%20measured%20a%20max%20of%201%2C500%20nits%20on%20the%20A95L%20in%20its%20%26quot%3BProfessional%26quot%3B%20picture%20mode%2C%20which%20offers%20the%20most%20accurate%20default%20image.%20That's%20500%20nits%20more%20than%20Sony's%20previous%20model%20in%20this%20series%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fsony-a95k-qd-oled-4k-tv-first-look%5C%22%3EA95K%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20brightest%20measurement%20we've%20ever%20recorded%20on%20an%20OLED%20TV.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20brightness%20works%20in%20tandem%20with%20the%20OLED%20screen's%20pixel-level%20contrast%20to%20deliver%20stunning%20HDR%20images.%20Some%20HDR%20videos%20are%20graded%20for%20a%20peak%20luminance%20above%201%2C000%20nits%2C%20so%20the%20A95L's%20ability%20to%20go%20over%20that%20number%20allows%20it%20to%20display%20bright%20highlights%20more%20accurately.%20This%20is%20especially%20true%20when%20watching%20Dolby%20Vision%20material%20since%20these%20videos%20give%20the%20TV%20specific%20guidance%20on%20how%20to%20scale%20color%20and%20contrast%20to%20best%20match%20the%20display's%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESony's%20picture%20processing%20also%20helps%20to%20give%20the%20TV%20unrivaled%20image%20accuracy%2C%20and%20even%20lower%20quality%20sources%2C%20like%20cable%20and%20HD%20streams%2C%20upscale%20nicely.%20And%20like%20all%20OLED%20TVs%2C%20the%20picture%20quality%20doesn't%20degrade%20when%20you%20sit%20to%20the%20side%20of%20the%20screen.%20Given%20its%20premium%20price%2C%20it's%20also%20no%20surprise%20that%20the%20A95L%20has%20some%20nice%20design%20flourishes%2C%20like%20a%20backlit%20remote%2C%20an%20adjustable%20stand%20that%20supports%20three%20orientations%20(high%2C%20low%2C%20and%20narrow)%2C%20and%20a%20webcam%20for%20video%20calls%20and%20gesture%20controls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGamers%20get%20full%20120Hz%20support%20when%20paired%20with%20a%20PS5%20or%20Xbox%20Series%20X%20console%2C%20but%20only%20two%20of%20the%20TV's%20HDMI%20ports%20have%20the%20required%20bandwidth%20for%20this%20feature.%20There's%20also%20no%20144Hz%20mode%20for%20PC%20gaming%2C%20which%20is%20something%20that%20Samsung%2C%20TCL%2C%20and%20Hisense%20offer%20on%20many%20of%20their%20top%20TVs.%20Still%2C%20it's%20difficult%20to%20find%20much%20fault%20with%20the%20A95L%2C%20given%20how%20incredible%20it%20looks.%20Most%20people%20are%20better%20off%20saving%20money%20with%20any%20of%20our%20other%20best%2075-inch%20TV%20picks%2C%20but%20this%20is%20the%20high-end%20TV%20to%20buy%20if%20you%20don't%20have%20any%20budget%20restrictions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENote%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%2077-inch%20A95L%20is%20temporarily%20out%20of%20stock%20at%20most%20retailers%2C%20but%20some%20list%20a%20mid-February%20date%20for%20new%20inventory.%20If%20you%20want%20a%20high-end%2077-inch%20OLED%20alternative%2C%20we%20recommend%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-63746-20%26h%3D4819bee867465a75b909943ebcb2ca65427ecd2dadbae8684d3a867fd795528b%26postID%3D65c53fdab1a0a2d07726e8c4%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fbest-75-inch-tvs%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fdp%252FB0BVWYRK3G%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELG%20G3%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20can't%20match%20the%20A95L's%20picture%20accuracy%20but%20has%20similar%20brightness%20capabilities.%20But%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20the%20G3%20is%20primarily%20designed%20for%20wall%20mounting%20and%20doesn't%20include%20a%20regular%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%208K%20display%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20going%20to%20buy%20an%208K%20TV%2C%2075%20inches%20is%20the%20smallest%20size%20you%20should%20consider.%20This%20is%20because%20the%20benefits%20of%208K%20resolution%20are%20only%20noticeable%20when%20you%20sit%20close%20to%20an%20extra-large%20screen.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%2075-inch%208K%20TVs%2C%20the%20Samsung%20QN900C%20is%20easily%20one%20of%20the%20best.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20QN900C's%208K%20display%20offers%20four%20times%20the%20total%20number%20of%20pixels%20that%20you'd%20get%20on%20a%204K%20TV.%20But%20even%20more%20impressive%20than%20its%20resolution%20is%20the%20display's%20excellent%20contrast%20and%20brightness%20capabilities.%20The%20TV%20has%20a%20Mini%20LED%20backlight%20with%20fantastic%20local%20dimming%20performance.%20This%20results%20in%20some%20of%20the%20best%20black%20levels%20we've%20ever%20seen%20outside%20an%20OLED%20TV%20and%20one%20of%20the%20brightest%20panels%20you%20can%20buy.%20During%2