0the%20company%20that%20she%20was%20sexually%20harassed%20at%20the%20June%202022%20Cannes%20Lions%20industry%20event%20in%20France%20by%20an%20employee%20at%20a%20marketing%20company%20and%20that%20TikTok%20%26quot%3Bfailed%20to%20respond%20appropriately.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPuris%20also%20noted%20in%20the%20suit%20that%20she%20had%20reported%20%26quot%3Bdiscriminatory%20treatment%26quot%3B%20she%20faced%20to%20her%20managers%20and%20HR%2C%20but%20that%20the%20company%2C%20%26quot%3Btaking%20its%20directives%20from%20the%20office%20in%20China%2C%20failed%20to%20take%20any%20corrective%20action.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228256%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22TikTok%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65133fee1c099d0019ad19bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3Ed3sign%2Fgetty%20images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20lawsuit%20says%20it%20'became%20very%20evident'%20that%20Puris%20was%20on%20Zhang's%20alleged%20'kill%20list'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EByteDance%20executives%2C%20including%20Zhang%2C%20started%20having%20more%20control%20of%20TikTok's%20day-to-day%20operations%20in%20late%202020%20and%20early%202021%20and%20it%20%26quot%3Bbecame%20clear%20immediately%26quot%3B%20that%20Zhang%20was%20%26quot%3Bdispleased%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20way%20Puris%20led%20presentations%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPuris%20%26quot%3Bcelebrated%20her%20team's%20successes%20and%20achievements%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20Zhang%20felt%20that%20was%20%26quot%3Binappropriate%26quot%3B%20because%20%26quot%3Bhe%20believes%20that%20women%20should%20always%20remain%20humble%20and%20express%20modesty%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%202021%2C%20it%20became%20very%20evident%20that%20Ms.%20Puris%20was%20on%20Lidong%20Zhang's%20'kill%20list%2C'%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%20%26quot%3BPart%20of%20Lidong%20Zhang's%20'kill%20list'%20approach%20was%20to%20build%20a%20case%20against%20any%20employee%20he%20placed%20on%20the%20list%20and%20instruct%20other%20employees%20to%20do%20the%20same.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPuris%20says%20that%20as%20a%20result%2C%20TikTok%20started%20%26quot%3Bminimizing%26quot%3B%20her%20role%20at%20the%20company%20and%20she%20was%20left%20out%20of%20important%20decisions%20that%20would%20impact%20her%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMs.%20Puris'%20health%20began%20to%20suffer%20under%20the%20stress%20and%20pressure%20placed%20on%20her%20after%20she%20became%20part%20of%20Lidong%20Zhang's%20'kill%20list%2C'%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20suffered%20health%20issues%20and%20needed%20numerous%20surgical%20procedures%20due%20to%20ulcers%2C%20migraines%2C%20and%20irritable%20bowel%20syndrome.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20says%20Puris%20was%20fired%20in%20September%202022%20for%20%26quot%3Bperformance%20reasons%26quot%3B%20days%20after%20she%20emailed%20the%20head%20of%20global%20human%20resources%20to%20again%20%26quot%3Bexpress%20concerns%26quot%3B%20about%20%26quot%3Bthe%20treatment%20of%20women%20at%20TikTok%2C%20age%20discrimination%2C%20the%20sexual%20harassment%20at%20Cannes%20Lion%20and%20the%20overall%20work%20environment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20woman%20who%20started%20her%20career%20in%201995%2C%20I%20was%20taught%20to%20be%20quiet%20if%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20successful.%20Gender%20discrimination%20and%20sexual%20harassment%20were%20commonplace%2C%20but%20speaking%20out%20was%20career%20suicide%2C%26quot%3B%20Puris%20told%20BI%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BWisdom%20has%20taught%20me%20that%20I%20no%20longer%20need%20to%20be%20silenced%20or%20afraid%20to%20fight%20for%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20attorneys%2C%20Marjorie%20Mesidor%20and%20Monica%20Hincken%2C%20added%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20%26quot%3Bby%20all%20metrics%2C%26quot%3B%20Puris%20was%20%26quot%3Benorm