r%20two%20by%20May%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fpress-releases.htm%3Fdtl%2F37511%2FFirst_meeting_of_the_IndiaMaldives_High_Level_Core_Group%5C%22%3EThe%20Indian%20external%20affair%E2%80%99s%20readout%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20however%2C%20did%20not%20give%20the%20details%20and%20merely%20said%20that%20both%20countries%20had%20%E2%80%9Cagreed%20on%20a%20set%20of%20mutually%20workable%20solutions%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Findian-coast-guard-boats-maldives-muizzu-opposition-parliament%5C%22%3EOn%20Monday%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Maldivian%20President%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20declared%20that%20India%20had%20agreed%20to%20%E2%80%9Cwithdraw%E2%80%9D%20its%20military%20personnel.%20That%20marked%20the%20first%20instance%20where%20the%20Maldives%20explicitly%20said%20that%20Indian%20personnel%20would%20be%20%E2%80%9Cwithdrawn%2C%E2%80%9D%20departing%20from%20the%20previous%20use%20of%20the%20ambiguous%20term%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-to-replace-military-personnel-operating-aircraft-helicopters-maldives%5C%22%3Ereplace%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20foreign%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20days%20later%2C%20India%20finally%20acknowledged%20that%20military%20personnel%20will%20be%20withdrawn%2C%20albeit%20without%20explicitly%20using%20that%20term.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20like%20to%20say%20that%20the%20present%20personnel%20will%20be%20replaced%20by%20competent%20Indian%20technical%20personnel%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20MEA%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20at%20the%20weekly%20briefing%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20expertise%20for%20operating%20these%20platforms%20are%20usually%20found%20among%20ex-servicemen%20who%20had%20operated%20such%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnnouncing%20the%20withdrawal%20in%20his%20inaugural%20speech%20at%20the%20opening%20of%20parliament%2C%20Muizzu%20noted%20that%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20Ind