s%2C%20there%20is%20a%20worrying%20lack%20of%20transparency%20about%20where%2C%20when%20and%20how%20long%20the%20disruption%20will%20continue%2C%20thereby%20affecting%20voters%E2%80%99%20right%20to%20information%20and%20potentially%20the%20transmission%20of%20results.%20Those%20who%20gave%20this%20order%20must%20be%20identified%20and%20held%20responsible%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20People%E2%80%99s%20Party%20(PPP)%20petitioned%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20Pakistan%20to%20take%20cognisance%20that%20the%20disruption%20of%20internet%20services%20would%20impact%20voter%20turnout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%E2%80%99s%20Central%20Election%20Cell%20in-charge%20Senator%20Taj%20Haider%20wrote%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20that%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20move%20to%20suspend%20mobile%20phone%20services%20on%20grounds%20of%20security%20concerns%20was%20%E2%80%98illegal%E2%80%99%2C%20as%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1391859%5C%22%3Eviolated%20a%202018%20court%20order%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20closure%20has%20also%20adversely%20affected%20reporting%20and%20responding%20to%20security%20incidents.%20One%20of%20our%20workers%20was%20shot%20dead%20in%20Mirpurkhas%20today%20and%20it%20was%20after%20an%20hour%20that%20we%20came%20to%20know%20about%20the%20murder%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20stated%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Flive%2Felections-2024%231811985%5C%22%3Eas%20reported%20by%20%3Ci%3EDawn%20News%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20media%20reports%2C%20at%20least%20nine%20people%2C%20including%20six%20security%20personnel%2C%20were%20killed%20in%20violent%20incidents%20reported%20across%20Pakistan%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20also%20claimed%20that%20%E2%80%9Call%20political%20parties%2C%20except%20PML-N%2C%20have%20objected%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20internet%20disruption.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20spite%20of