%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReliance%20Industries%3C%2Fa%3E%20conglomerate%20headquartered%20in%20Mumbai.%20The%20rest%20of%20the%20ranking%E2%80%99s%20top%2010%20is%20a%20mix%20of%20different%20industries%2C%20countries%20and%20also%20one%20global%20household%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ambanis%E2%80%99%20wealth%20remains%20more%20than%20double%20that%20of%20the%20next%20clan%20in%20the%20ranking%20of%20Asia%E2%80%99s%20richest%20families%2C%20the%20Hartonos%20of%20Indonesia%E2%80%99s%20Djarum%20brand.%20It%20also%20earns%20them%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Ffeatures%2F2023-worlds-richest-families%2F%3Fembedded-checkout%3Dtrue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erank%208%20%3C%2Fa%3Eamong%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20wealthiest%20legacy%20families.%20All%20in%20all%2C%20the%202024%20ranking%20now%20features%20four%20Indian%20families%20in%20the%20top%2010%2C%20up%20from%20just%20two%20last%20year.%20New%20additions%20are%20the%20Jindal%20family%2C%20who%20made%20their%20wealth%20in%20different%20industrial%20sectors%2C%20and%20Birla%20family%2C%20who%20run%20conglomerate%20Aditya%20Birla%20Group.%20Two%20families%20each%20hailing%20from%20Hong%20Kong%20and%20Thailand%20are%20also%20among%20the%20top%2010%2C%20with%20Thai%20Red%20Bull%20inventors%2C%20the%20Yoovidhyas%2C%20in%20rank%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChinese%20emigrants%20are%20quite%20common%20among%20the%20list%20of%20Asia%E2%80%99s%20most%20wealthy%20families.%20Chearavanont%20patriarch%20Chia%20Ek%20Chor%20came%20to%20Thailand%20from%20Southern%20China%20in%201921%20and%20started%20out%20importing%20and%20exporting%20seeds%2C%20vegetables%20and%20animal%20products%20between%20Bangkok%2C%20China%20and%20Hong%20Kong.%20Outside%20of%20the%20top%2010%2C%20the%20Pao%2FWoo%20family%20(rank%2011)%20and%20the%20inventors%20of%20Oyster%20Sauce%2C%20the%20Lee%20family%20(rank%2017)%2C%20made%20their%20fortunes%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20a