ehsaas%20jatata%20hai%20ki%20isne%20galat%20kiya.%20Aur%20usko%20pyar%20ho%20jata%20hai.%20Yeh%20sab%20kya%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%20(I%20would%20like%20to%20say%20to%20that%20woman%2C%20'Go%20ask%20Aamir%20Khan%2C%20'Is%20she%20like%20a%20pillar%2C%20a%20girl%2C%20or%20a%20firecracker%3F'%20What%20was%20that%3F%26quot%3B%20Then%20come%20back%20to%20me.%20If%20you%20remember%20Dil%2C%20he%20almost%20creates%20the%20situation%20towards%20an%20attempted%20rape%2C%20and%20it%20makes%20her%20realise%20that%20she%20was%20wrong.%20She%20ultimately%20falls%20in%20love.%20What%20is%20all%20this%3F)%20I%20don't%20understand%20why%20they%20attack%20like%20that%20before%20checking%20the%20surroundings%2C%26quot%3B%20Sandeep%20Reddy%20Vanga%20told%20Dainik%20Bhaskar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAAMIR%20KHAN'S%20OLD%20APOLOGY%20GOES%20VIRAL%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20Mr%20Vanga's%20remarks%20went%20viral%2C%20the%20Internet%20went%20digging%20and%20found%20an%20old%20video%20of%20Aamir%20Khan%20apologising%20for%20%3Cem%3EDil%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3EKhambe%20Jaisi%20Khadi%20Hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20song.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20very%20ashamed%2C%26quot%3B%20Aamir%20had%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Aaj%20Tak%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3EDil%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20co-starred%20Madhuri%20Dixit%2C%20was%20a%20huge%20hit%20but%20has%20since%20been%20accused%20of%20rape%20apology%20and%20trivializing%20sexual%20assault%20as%20a%20form%20of%20romance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAamir%20Khan%20said%20in%20the%20old%20interview%3A%20%26quot%3BHindi%20films%20have%20not%20been%20responsible%20enough%2C%20especially%20the%20way%20we%20project%20men%20and%20women.%20When%20we%20show%20something%20wrong%20in%20the%20films%2C%20we%20also%20show%20that%20the%20result%20of%20it%20is%20something%20positive.%20Which%20is%20wrong.%20And%20we%20often%20make%20the%20women%20an%20'item'%20in%20films.%20Even%20the%20songs%20are%20like%20'%3Cem%3Etu%20cheez%20badi%20hai%20mast%20mast%3