eaking%20creations%20are%20the%20result%20of%20the%20ingenuity%20of%20finalists%2C%20children%20ranging%20from%20Classes%206%20to%209%2C%20who%20participated%20in%20L%26amp%3BT%E2%80%99s%20National%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330277%2Fbengaluru-startup-stemonsters-founder-dr-sonali-dasgupta-making-science-fun-for-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESTEM%20Challenge%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%94%20a%20culmination%20of%20the%20conglomerate%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Engineering%20Futures%E2%80%99%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaunched%20in%202020%2C%20this%20initiative%20aims%20to%20cultivate%20science%2C%20technology%2C%20engineering%2C%20and%20mathematics%20(STEM)%20interest%20among%20school%20children.%20By%20reaching%20out%20to%20schools%20that%20lack%20access%20to%20STEM%20labs%2C%20children%20in%20remote%20corners%20of%20the%20country%20are%20now%20able%20to%20enhance%20their%20scientific%20knowledge%2C%20grasp%20essential%20concepts%2C%20and%20develop%20problem-solving%20skills%20for%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20school%20teachers%2C%20the%20remarkable%20outcome%20of%20this%20initiative%20is%20that%20even%20children%20who%20typically%20struggled%20in%20exams%20are%20now%20able%20to%20unleash%20their%20creativity%20and%20understand%20science%20concepts%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that%20traditional%20teaching%20methods%20often%20fall%20short%20of%20achieving.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20challenge%20winners%20%E2%80%94%20Joshwa%20A%20and%20Sivakarthikeyan%20N%20from%20Class%208%20at%20Government%20High%20School%2C%20Gerugambakkam%2C%20Chennai%20%E2%80%94%20ingeniously%20crafted%20the%20agricultural%20tricycle%20by%20repurposing%20an%20old%20cycle%2C%20scrap%20metal%2C%20and%20wheels%20acquired%20from%20a%20local%20scrap%20shop.%20Their%20teacher%2C%20Thenmughil%20Ramakrishnan%2C%20was%20initially%20surprised%20to%20see%20the%20boys%20transporting%20scrap%20materials%20to