%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20boost%20the%20initiative%20and%20provide%20students%20with%20a%20platform%20to%20showcase%20their%20talents%2C%20L%26amp%3BT%20initiated%20STEM%20fests%20beginning%20in%20October%202023.%20Over%206%2C000%20students%20from%20Classes%206%20to%209%20actively%20participated%20in%20intra%20and%20inter-school%20level%20competitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20STEM%20model-making%20competition%20featured%20interesting%20themes%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20green%20and%20sustainable%20energy%2C%20waste%20management%2C%20smart%20schools%2C%20and%20satellite%20and%20launch%20vehicles.%20From%20these%20themes%2C%20208%20teams%20were%20selected%20for%20the%20regional%20level%20competition%2C%20and%20ultimately%2C%2024%20teams%20from%20cities%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Chennai%2C%20Coimbatore%2C%20Hazira%2C%20Vadodara%2C%20Talegaon%2C%20and%20Mumbai%20%E2%80%94%20advanced%20to%20the%20finale%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EL%26amp%3BT%E2%80%99s%20employee%20volunteers%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20mentoring%20and%20assisting%20students%2C%20helping%20them%20refine%20and%20perfect%20their%20models%20for%20the%20competitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Government%20High%20School%2C%20Gerugambakkam%2C%20Chennai%2C%20won%20the%20challenge%2C%20while%20the%20Government%20High%20School%2C%20Velappanchavudi%2C%20Chennai%20and%20Shree%20Kanchanlal%20Mamawala%20Surat%20Municipal%20Corporation%20School%20(Hazira%2C%20Gujarat)%20emerged%20as%20the%20first%20and%20second%20runners-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20winning%20schools%20received%20cash%20rewards%20%E2%80%94%20Rs%2050%2C000%20for%20the%20national%20champion%2C%20Rs%2030%2C000%20for%20the%20first%20runner-up%2C%20and%20Rs%2020%2C000%20for%20the%20second%20runner-up%20%E2%80%94%20to%20facilitate%20the%20upgrading%20of%20their%20science%20labs.%20Additionally%2C%20all%20three%20winning%20teams%20were%20presented%20with%20telescopes%2C%20drones%20and%20a%20DIY%20Robotics%20Kit%2C%20providing%20them%20with%20further%20exposure%20to%20STEM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20special%20opportunity%2C%20the%20winning%20teams%20were%20invited%20to%20visit%20L%26amp%3BT%E2%80%99s%20tech%20projects%20and%20engage%20in%20interactions%20with%20the%20leadership%20team%2C%20enriching%20their%20understanding%20and%20appreciation%20of%20real-world%20applications%20in%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20block%20level%20coding%20workshop%20organised%20by%20AIF%2C%20Class%207%20students%20%E2%80%94%20Santhosh%20M%20and%20Yuvan%20Shankar%20Raja%20K%20from%20Government%20High%20School%2C%20Velappanchavadi%2C%20Chennai%20%E2%80%94%20tackled%20the%20topic%20of%20waste%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG20240203113800-min-1707141244-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20modern%20waste%20segregating%20system%20made%20by%20students%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG20240203113800-min-1707141244-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG20240203113800-min-1707141244-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG20240203113800-min-1707141244-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG20240203113800-min-1707141244-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG20240203113800-min-1707141244-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG20240203113800-min-1707141244-1536x1536.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG20240203113800-min-1707141244-2048x2048.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F202