0with%20and%20sell%20products%20from%20over%20100%20healthy%20brands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhana%20states%20that%20they%20will%20achieve%20gross%20sales%20of%20Rs%20100%20crore%20this%20year%20and%20wants%20to%20become%20a%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore%20company%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98An%20ode%20to%20my%20mother%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201083px)%20100vw%2C%201083px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen7-1706874286.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221083%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ahana%20studied%20at%20Harvard%20Business%20School%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen7-1706874286.jpeg%201083w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen7-1706874286-227x300.jpeg%20227w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen7-1706874286-500x660.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen7-1706874286-768x1014.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOpen7-1706874286-150x198.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340618%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221430%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAhana%20studied%20at%20Harvard%20Business%20School.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpen%20Secret%E2%80%99s%20USP%2C%20besides%20its%20snacks%2C%20is%20its%20women%2C%20says%20Ahana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20factories%20are%20run%20by%20200%20women%20and%20over%2050%20percent%20of%20its%20employees%20are%20women.%20Why%3F%20Ahana%20believes%20that%20women%20leaders%20like%20her%2C%20who%20are%20privileged%2C%20must%20provide%20opportunities%20to%20women.%20After%20all%2C%20it%20was%20due%20to%20her%20mother%E2%80%99s%20belief%20that%20thi