Now%20a%20psychotherapist%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20Heal%20Grow%20Thrive%20Foundation%2C%20Mansi%20engages%20in%20heartfelt%20conversations%20to%20open%20up%20about%20her%20healing%20journey%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Abuse%20became%20my%20normal%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20Mansi%E2%80%99s%20childhood%20was%20challenging%2C%20to%20say%20the%20least.%20%E2%80%9CGrowing%20up%20in%20Kolkata%20in%20a%20joint%20family%20setup%20was%20challenging%2C%20but%20it%20became%20even%20harder%20when%20my%20grandfather%20passed%20away%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20father%E2%80%99s%20side%20of%20the%20family%20wanted%20my%20grandmother%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327071%2Fvaranasi-ias-officer-himanshu-nagpal-mission-muskaan-reunites-lost-children-with-families%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ego%20to%20Banaras%20%5BVaranasi%5D%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20live%20her%20days%20as%20a%20widow.%20My%20grandmother%20had%20to%20essentially%20fight%20for%20her%20survival%20and%20place%20in%20the%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Mansi%20was%20too%20young%20to%20perceive%20the%20patriarchy%20her%20childhood%20home%20was%20seeped%20in%2C%20she%20recalls%20her%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20suffering.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20a%20child%2C%20this%20is%20a%20traumatic%20experience.%20Even%20today%2C%20I%20try%20to%20break%20down%20that%20instance%20and%20understand%20how%20it%20affected%20me%20as%20a%20person%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F246155%2Fbihar-patna-wedding-gurhathi-parents-defying-patriarchy-ritual-viral-story-twitter-div200%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epatriarc