%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETherapy%20was%20not%20very%20popular%3C%2Fa%3E%20back%20then%20and%20she%20found%20it%20very%20difficult%20to%20get%20a%20job%20anywhere.%20%E2%80%9CI%20noticed%20that%20while%20there%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20graduates%20of%20psychology%2C%20there%20was%20no%20place%20for%20them%20to%20start%20their%20careers.%20This%20is%20how%20the%20Heal%20Grow%20Thrive%20Foundation%20came%20into%20being.%20Since%20we%20are%20self-funded%2C%20the%20therapy%20is%20done%20for%20a%20small%20fee%20but%20what%20we%20focus%20on%20is%20healing%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20fleet%20of%2020%20young%20and%20budding%20therapists%2C%20she%20has%20helped%20over%20500%20survivors%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20patient%20of%20Mansi%20who%20prefers%20to%20be%20anonymous%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20talked%20to%20Mansi%2C%20she%20created%20a%20safe%20space%20for%20me.%20It%20was%20a%20space%20where%20I%20could%20really%20be%20%E2%80%98me%E2%80%99.%20I%20did%20not%20understand%20how%20much%20I%20needed%20the%20help%20until%20I%20took%20it.%20The%20best%20thing%20is%20that%20she%20focussed%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98why%E2%80%99%20instead%20of%20turning%20to%20medication.%20Why%20was%20I%20feeling%20a%20certain%20way%2C%20why%20is%20the%20trauma%20so%20deeply%20rooted%2C%20and%20what%20I%20can%20do%20to%20help%20myself%3F%20I%20am%20glad%20that%20I%20took%20the%20step%20for%20myself.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMansi%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20main%20focal%20point%20of%20my%20practice%20is%20to%20heal%20by%20processing%20things.%20As%20a%20survivor%20and%20a%20psychologist%2C%20I%20know%20how%20taking%20medicine%20can%20feel%20like%20a%20way%20out.%20However%2C%20I%20sincerely%20believe%20in%20trying%20everything%20in%20my%20power%20before%20referring%20patients%20to%20a%20psychiatrist.%20We%20believe%20in%20creating%20a%20safe%20space%20for%20the%20trauma%20survivor%20and%20helping%20them%20heal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20how%20healing%20is%20not%20linear%2C%20she%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CEven%20though%20I%20am%20an%20adult%20out%20of%20that%20house%20and%20all%20the%20trauma%20it%20brought%2C%20I%20still%20get%20stuck%20in%20toxic%20cycles.%20I%20am%20happy%20that%20I%20am%20away%20from%20it%2C%20but%20I%20still%20believe%20that%20healing%20is%20not%20linear%20and%20you%20can%20always%20slip%20back.%20I%20still%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20isolate%20myself%20and%20disassociate%20from%20my%20body.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC1Ujj20yvra%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC1Ujj20yvra%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC1Ujj20yvra%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Mansi%20Poddar%7C%20Psychotherapist%20(%40healwithmansi)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20what%20is%20important%20is%20the%20first%20step%20towards%20healing.%20Once%20you%20reach%20there%2C%20you%20will%20start%20to%20get%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20anyone%20who%20is%20suffering%20as%20she%20did%20in%20the%20past%2C%20Mansi%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20believe%2C%20more%20than%20anything%2C%20that%20parents%20should%20read%20and%20comprehend%20the%20importance%20of%20not%20stigmatising%20mental%20health.%20It%E2%80%99s%20crucial%20for%20parents%20to%20advocate%20for%20their%20kids%2C%20not%20necessarily%20through%20confrontations%20with%20teachers%20and%20others%2C%20but%20by%20genuinely%20sitting%20down%20with%20their%20children%20and%20understanding%20their%20perspective.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20message%20is%20directed%20towards%20parents%2C%20teachers%2C%20and%20adults%20in%20general%2C%20urging%20them%20to%20become%20more%20trauma-informed.%20It%E2%80%99s%20essential%20to%20recognise%20what%20might%20be%20traumatic%20for%20a%20child%20and%20to%20avoid%20hindering%20their%20access%20to%20mental%20health%20care.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20%3Cem%3EAll%20pictures%20courtesy%3A%20Mansi%20Poddar)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706797215000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fmansi-1-1706795794.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D340517%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mansi%20Poddar%2C%20a%20psychologist%20and%20therapist%2C%20survived%20domestic%20violence%2C%20molestation%20and%20abuse.%20With%20her%20Heal%20Grow%20Thrive%20Foundation%2C%20she%20helps%20survivors%20heal%20from%20their%20trauma.%20In%20a%20candid%20conversation%2C%20Mansi%20shares%20her%20experiences%20and%20the%20lessons%20she%20learned.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22TechForGood%20India%20Conclave%3