5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20unique%20approach%20involves%20incorporating%20snippets%20from%20web%20series%20and%20TV%20shows%20to%20make%20learning%20engaging%20and%20fun.%20Overcoming%20some%20initial%20trolling%2C%20Dhiraj%E2%80%99s%20follower%20count%20rose%20from%20160%20on%207%20December%202023%20to%201%20million%20on%2020%20January%202024%E2%80%94barely%2044%20days%E2%80%94on%20Instagram.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20over%201%20million%20followers%20today%2C%20Dhiraj%20has%20risen%20out%20of%20obscurity%20through%20his%20creativity%2C%20passion%20and%20desire%20to%20improve%20his%20communication%20skills%20by%20teaching%20others%20how%20to%20talk%20like%20a%20native%20English%20speaker%20despite%20lacking%20the%20resources%20that%20most%20content%20creators%20possess.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20spoke%20to%20Dhiraj%20to%20dig%20a%20little%20deeper%20into%20his%20magical%20journey%20on%20the%20internet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC2TyPKJABP-%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC2TyPKJABP-%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C